7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Listnr and Voicemod share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Speech. Where Listnr pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Multilingual and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Voicemod uniquely offers Custom Voices and Real Time, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Listnr holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Voicemod scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Voicemod comes in at a lower starting price of $4/mo, while Listnr begins at $9/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Listnr's free tier and Voicemod's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
